{"tid":1368602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[三毛洗地警號] 聽日出去嘅手足小心周圍有人「忽然勇武」","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:39:48.000Z","uid":131125,"like":125,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"23d6f80cbee7327abfa58044cfe25cb611f42f19","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1368182/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1368182/page/1</a><br />\n勇武少一個就少一個，點解你哋又要建立2014左膠大台？！？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1368409/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1368409/page/1</a><br />\n你班仆街冚家鏟聽日夠膽割勇武蓆，我地就夠薑以後唔撚保護和理非！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1367565/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1367565/page/1</a><br />\n一味叫人和平嗰啲食屎啦<br />\n<br />\n今日一直都有好多post話叫人唔好阻住勇武、唔好割席/篤灰勇武、和理非唔好起大台阻住勇武<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">意圖污名化勇武手足</span>，同埋藉住呢次727又分化勇武同埋和理非<br />\n佢地嘅留言好多時都係重覆又重覆「和理非無用」「勇武攞條命出黎一定要掩護好」等論點<br />\n但從來唔能夠明確指出<span style=\"color: red;\">「想做咩」「目標係咩」「為左咩而做」</span><br />\n<br />\n呢度再次釐清一下點解呢次運動入面勇武同和理非不再分化<br />\n1、14年雨傘運動嘅前車可鑒<br />\n2、目標明確，理念明確<br />\n以612為例，前線勇武係為左阻止二讀，阻止立法會繼續開會<br />\n同埋爭取衝入立法會令佢停止運動<br />\n又以71為例，雖然立法會已經休會<br />\n但當時比較大部份嘅聲音都認為唔能夠坐以待斃(當日早上阻止升旗失敗)<br />\n所以有人去下半旗換黑旗，而有人就開始衝擊立法會<br />\n目的是藉佔據立法會呢個具有象徵意義嘅政府建築物黎做更進一步嘅事情(宣言)<br />\n<br />\n所以見到上面果啲洗地post，其實可以睇到果啲樓主不停漫罵同指責<br />\n扮哂情緒激動咁將「釐清概念同解釋原因」嘅責任推得一乾二淨(同何妖一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n推足咁多頁鬧足咁多頁都無清楚講到<span style=\"color: red;\">「想做咩」「目標係咩」「為左咩而做」</span><br />\n奈何見到果啲post咁多正皮真係擔心有啲人睇完記左入腦正皮完就算，影響到聽日行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以聽日入元朗嘅手足請緊慎<br />\n如果見到周圍有人主動出手好似想衝想做大事咁<br />\n記得問清楚佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">「想做咩」「目標係咩」「為左咩而做」</span><br />\n如果聽過合情又合理嘅絕對可以周圍宣傳呼籲叫人join自己又join埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果佢地粒聲唔出，又或者都係流於情緒eg「咪撚阻住前線衝啦」<br />\n又完全解釋唔到做緊咩野，或者講啲野出黎1999一聽都已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就要考慮下阻止佢地嘅必要性啦</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">考慮過覺得緊急就要阻止啦</span></span><br />\n重申多次，勇武唔等於魯莽，亦唔等於無謀同埋無腦<br />\n溝通唔到嘅話好可能佢自己都解釋唔通，<span style=\"color: red;\">例如接左order做野嘅人就會咁</span><br />\n相反如果解釋得通而手足又okay嘅話，其實唔抗拒加入埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點解今次要咁緊要優先去考慮任何嘅勇武行動係咪合邏輯<br />\n就可以延順閱讀下面巴絲嘅post："},{"pid":"19b3c92d9122160905fa91e99192b358cd9fb529","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"放漏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1367816/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1367816/page/1</a><br />\n一味覺得聽日一定要發生衝突既食屎喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1368347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1368347/page/1</a><br />\nAO: 政府透過727示威暴力升級抹黑示威者與白衫無異<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1368146/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1368146/page/1</a><br />\n【一班AO的分享】"},{"pid":"9ab702364689454c959a12215b83e82894d58a20","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"支持請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546e410aa0f58c91b590792c56237e7cfc972ac6","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:53:39.000Z","msg":"仲有呼籲下巴絲以後睇POST諗一陣先再正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到果啲睇落正路，但其實諗落極恐怖嘅post有咁多正皮就驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b642c71a5367874596c405a621acf389eda769c","tid":1368602,"uid":283021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"我預計聽日會有假勇武或假白衣人挑起事端"},{"pid":"6e96a715e114c025b6ae274f5fba30f9cb8ac57e","tid":1368602,"uid":182994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"［急！］元朗撚一定要入嚟 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f0775ea6ef5814455455aea250acc2c6b69daf9","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8b642c71a5367874596c405a621acf389eda769c","tid":1368602,"uid":283021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"我預計聽日會有假勇武或假白衣人挑起事端"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"應該會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家連喺連登打口水交見到「割席篤灰」都會覺得有無搞錯<br />\n聽日現場一定更加難分係咪應該阻止<br />\n<br />\n對家好清楚，割席同篤灰係我地曾經嘅一個傷疤<br />\n一掂到呢樣野就會盲目去諗「割席篤灰唔應該」<br />\n而忽略左交流溝通嘅重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefe77fec4453cedd0bb3190aab8a228cd9d14b7","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84d7f3b29147320270b76b20608982c9f58440d6","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2409929189689f5c0028e41f1b98d80ad894405","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:59:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b4c0d5f17e92012841e06d4febd296b1914c440","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:59:54.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"45019f2c2699ed807bbdca992cb527587271ed18","tid":1368602,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"不割蓆 不分化"},{"pid":"150b0dd14c659dc4963f6741dcba4ecb84da4bfc","tid":1368602,"uid":124859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:00:28.000Z","msg":"係大馬路有勇武有咩問題？<br />\n入村就話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57c5deb436628dff9f6f97db80687ca7d70b17d","tid":1368602,"uid":282490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武 唔等於無腦！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n各位和理非+勇武手足，如果見到無腦想衝嘅，可以合理地判斷佢地係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e8f891d64f32e5a4df544fcd0e6790daf3b49e","tid":1368602,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"要睇路啦 各位 呢場戰役 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0318e122192fbb731588cc9e81304d6df4a1b04","tid":1368602,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"全力推<br />\n不割席<br />\n力量用黎保護自己保護手足"},{"pid":"bfdf580951f8b702918693efa39fa72da73e822b","tid":1368602,"uid":281904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"好多人誤以為「不分化」唔代表「前線做乜都得」，聽日醒水"},{"pid":"a11f34792cc4b4b1f4a10aa1c34a1a7a99aafe7e","tid":1368602,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f4dd1a52529712d8199e5ee043c7185b40e5f89","tid":1368602,"uid":281904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfdf580951f8b702918693efa39fa72da73e822b","tid":1368602,"uid":281904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"好多人誤以為「不分化」唔代表「前線做乜都得」，聽日醒水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:02:46.000Z","msg":"*代表，自膠"},{"pid":"2bcea15c96eea9962c5306d990adf50ee06ddc8e","tid":1368602,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"各位手足出門前睇下有冇帶漏嘢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g